attributes.title: Traveling to Exhibitor show
attributes.description:
Created on March 11, 2010 by znzn on Sourcemap.org:

This is a Travel Map that calculates C02e for one passenger, one way, from Connecticut to Las Vegas.  The default weight of one passenger is 97kg.  This weight is only an average that also accounts for baggage.
